## 4. Benefits of API integration 
1. Real-world skill: Every business needs to connect to Stripe, Shopify, OpenAI, etc.
2. Dynamic data: Prices update automatically instead of hardcoded.
3. Error handling: try/except + raise_for_status() makes it production ready.

## 5. Learning Points. 
1. requests library: Industry standard for HTTP calls.
2. Error handling: Always wrap API calls in try/except. Networks fail.
3. raise_for_status(): Catches 404, 500 errors automatically.
4. Separation of concerns: API logic lives in api_client.py, not mixed in business logic.
5. Public APIs: Use FakeStoreAPI, JSONPlaceholder for portfolio projects. No API key needed.

